        * c-tree.h (struct lang_type): Rename 'objc_protocols' field

[gcc/cp/ChangeLog]
2004-12-07  Ziemowit Laski  <zlaski@apple.com>

        * cp-tree.h (struct lang_type_class): Rename 'objc_protocols'
        field to 'objc_info'.
